name: Adrian Lamo
tweet: @AllThingsNatSec If you want my cynical opinion, it was either too minor (at the time), or they were building evidence to *make* it a federal case. The Bureau doesn't like sharing with other agencies, or even having to ask them for help.

name: Adrian Lamo
tweet: @AllThingsNatSec In theory SAR => FBI => Fusion Center => Local authorities (in this case). You pick up the phone. It wasn't FBI's *fault*, but they got hit with bystander effect.
